data.description: Marvelous house. LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION!! This 4 Bedroom, 2 bath home is conveniently  located community of Orangewood. This home has been well cared for and offers an updated Kitchen  with new cabinets, back splash, solid surface counter tops, gas range & closet pantry, NEW ROOF, NEW  PLUMBING, Huge great room with vaulted ceilings, large enough to accommodate dining area as well  if desired. Split bedroom plan; second bath has new vanity, sink, mirror & fixtures. Tile & laminate  floors throughout. Enclosed lanai across entire back of house, 32x11, features wall A/C unit so room  can be enjoyed all year round. Huge corner lot, completely fenced, with patio and wood deck, large  storage shed on concrete pad. HOA is optional, but you will want to join to use the common areas,  tennis court, playground, and picnic area around the lake. This home is close to great shopping areas  and restaurants, plus John Young, OBT, 417 and other major roadways. Disney, Sea World, OIA, and  Downtown Orlando are just minutes away. Act quick as it will not last longer.
